    "body": "Thanks for the issue.\r\n\r\nYou're looking at the wrong condition. It's `voteStart.isPending()` that determines whether the Governor moves onto `Active` state. So when the block is advanced to \"snapshot\" (i.e. `voteStart.deadline`), it is no longer `Pending` and moves onto `Active`.\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/OpenZeppelin/openzeppelin-contracts/blob/1b27c13096d6e4389d62e7b0766a1db53fbb3f1b/contracts/governance/Governor.sol#L118",
